<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span> صحيح ـ <span class="c2">((الروض النضير)</span>) <span class="c2">(١٥٤)</span>، <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٨٨٩)</span>: ق.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>